If you're returning for a refund, please be aware we refund the purchase price but not the original or return shipping. If you didn't pay a separate shipping cost, we'll refund the purchase price. Policies.Pricing: We strive to price competitively, but we're always open to negotiating. If you're looking for a better deal, contact us and we'll see what we can do.
Policies.Feedback: Like other independent ebay sellers, we thrive on positive feedback, which highlights a seller's integrity to potential buyers. Our commitment to our buyers is the same - we always leave positive feedback after a good selling experience as a measure of our appreciation. If you purchase from us and you feel we've fallen short in any way, please contact us before leaving negative feedback. We hate seeing a buyer end up dissatisfied with their purchase, and we'll go the extra mile to make it right.
